content: Hello. (Looks down at hands in lap, fingers tapping once on fabric) It’s... good to be here. The drive in was quiet. No traffic on the 101 this morning.

I’m... managing. The blueprints are due Thursday. I haven’t finalized the structural calculations yet. (Shifts gaze to pen on table, fingers tap twice) Sleep’s been... inconsistent. Waking up at 3 a.m. to check email. It’s not a big deal. (Pauses, voice flattens) Do you build homes? The foundation settling thing… it’s funny how that happens.
